[normal]              
[normal]Q176[bold] 
[normal]Chair:[bold] I am dancing around the issue of the fact that responsibility to protect is a UN concept and when it was drawn up it was always envisaged that it would have the backing of the Security Council. That was at the world summit that gave birth to the concept. 
